==Trivia==
*According to [[Noodle|Noodle Fideu]], the penguins were set up with their costume by [[Rotini]], and they had "ome trubble wi' flyin' yeller amfibians on the walk down", which means that they were mistaken for [[Sick-looking sheep]] and someone tried to shoot a [[yellow toad]] at them.{{CitePostbag |issue=19 |letter=Letter 6|author=Noodle Fideu}}
*During the [[Sheep Shearer]] quest, [[Fred the Farmer]] says: "''Some say it's a black hearted shapeshifter, hungering for the souls of hard working decent folk like me. Others say it's just a sheep.''" This is likely a reference to ''The Thing'' in the 1982 film, {{WP|The Thing (1982 film)|The Thing}}.

